b2\u950b2\u6539.gif?t=1726626882\" /><br><br><u><strong>Alliance or Hostility?</strong></u><br>Declare war, or make peace and team up with rival factions utilizing diplomacy tactics. V1.0 introduces more diversity to social relationships and tribal affairs across the land, adding AI rebellions, tribal titles and a new Favor system between NPCs.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094520/extras/\u5927\u5730\u56fe\u9047\u654c.gif?t=1726626882\" /><br><br><u><strong>What\u2019s More in 1.0 Launch</strong></u><br>Discover the free-to-explore Sandbox mode, brand-new UI experiences, reworkings of character skills and arms units across the board, more dynamic social relations and Tavern Brawling, magical jewel packs, additional side quests and more!","developers":["\u6c49\u5bb6\u677e\u9f20Han-Squirrel Studio"],"dlc":[2406290,1849490,2265790,1416310,2621910],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1094520/header.jpg?t=1726626882","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256865227,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256865227/movie480.mp4?t=1639624552","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256865227/movie_max.mp4?t=1639624552"},"name":"Full launch trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256865227/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1639624552","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/2